org.nsdl.mptstore
Class TestConfig

java.lang.Object
  org.nsdl.mptstore.TestConfig

public abstract class TestConfig
extends Object

Provides static access to test configuration. The source of the test configuration is the test.properties file, which is exprected to be located in the directory indicated by the test.dir system property.

Author:
cwilper@cs.cornell.edu

getTestDatabase

public static String getTestDatabase()
Get the name of the database we're testing. This is the value of the test.database system property. For this NAME, the following system properties should also be defined:
  • test.NAME.driver
  • test.NAME.url
  • test.NAME.username
  • test.NAME.password
